gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

This is prepared for a dance, open it, no one knows how to tie; 
Rama Chandra has sat calmly, pleased with God's arrival, rejoiced.

Here is the translation:

They have come without a shadow or destruction, making their own home; 
Their kinkur has been said to be awake, it has become thus in your house.

Here is the translation:

He has given a hint to Vaidyraaj, saying "You have come, O Great One"; 
He said that he has given me this sign; how will you sleep when I am gone?

Here is the translation:

I have seen someone's downfall, kept in mind a human's defeat; 
This I said to Shobharam when, written by me without pride that time.
